fields.descriptive_line: Office, panelled room designed by Frank Lloyd Wright, Pittsburgh, USA, 1937.
fields.physical_description: Office, panelled room of swamp cypress plywood.
fields.title: Frank Lloyd Wright Room; Kaufmann Office
fields.public_access_description: Frank Lloyd Wright (1867-1959) designed this panelled office for the Kaufmann Department Store in Pittsburgh, USA. He also designed the furniture, carpets and upholstery.
fields.production_note:
The office and furniture were designed for the Kaufmann Department Store, Pittsburgh.

Reason For Production: Commission
